T16TD4441E:353b-0: @353b * // lha dbang phyug gis tshogs bdag la gnang ba'i sa mu dra pha la'i sbyor ba kha bsgyur dang bcas pa ni /
T16TD4441E:353b-1: de yang thog mar sa mu dra pha la mang nyung ci rigs pa rdza snod gtsang mar blug la zhag bdun gyi bar ra'i chus spangs te khu ba pho //
T16TD4441E:353b-2: de grib bskams byas la zha thag chod pa dang /
T16TD4441E:353b-3: slar yang ba'i chus zhag bdun /
T16TD4441E:353b-4: bangga ra'i khu bas zhag bdun /
T16TD4441E:353b-5: ni ra gunda'i khu bas zhag bzhi /
T16TD4441E:353b-6: da dhu ra'i khu bas zhag gsum /
T16TD4441E:353b-7: 'bras chu skyur mos zhag gcig rnams spangs skems gong ltar rim bzhin byas la /
T16TD4441E:353b-8: de nas zhib par btags la thun tshad nyis 'gyur tsam re ni ra gunda'i khu bas rta byas btang bas mdze rigs brgyad gang gis na yang rtsa ba nas thon zhing khong skran dang yan lag khol bur skrangs pa zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:353b-9: ra'i chus rta byas khong du btang zhing dpral bar byugs na mgo bo na ba la phan no //
T16TD4441E:353b-10: ra'i chur brdar te mig la byugs na ling tog med par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:353b-11: shel dkar dang mnyam du btang na bud med bu btsas pa'i bang tshad sel bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:353b-12: ra'i chus rta byas btang na mkhris pa'i nad thams cad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354a-0: ba'i dar ba dang mnyam du btang na pho ba na zhing spos @354a * //
T16TD4441E:354a-2: aa dza wa na dang mnyam du zos na dug rigs mtha' dag la phan no //
T16TD4441E:354a-3: hinggu dang mnyam du zos na srin nad zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354a-4: ha ri tal btul ma dang mnyam du zos na mdze dkar po thon par 'gyur zhing rma gsar rnying thams cad la phan no ;
T16TD4441E:354a-5: / ni mbu'i khu bas rta byas btang na pho ba'i gzer zhi (la la phud) bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354a-6: nimbu'i 'bru dang mnyam du (shing kun) btang na mkhris pa'i nad thams cad la phan no /
T16TD4441E:354a-7: (ba ba la/) ha la dhi dang mnyam du btang kyang phan yon gong dang 'dra /
T16TD4441E:354a-8: ra'i chus rta byas btang na lus stobs che zhing mdangs dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354a-9: kungku ma'i khu ba dang mnyam du btang na skya rbab la phan no //
T16TD4441E:354a-10: yang gur gum gyi khu bas rta byas khong du btang zhing rna bar yang blug na rna ba 'on (sga ser) pas thos par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354a-11: ra'i chu la brdar nas mig la byugs na srod long sel lo ;
T16TD4441E:354a-12: / ra'i chus rta byas btang na dbugs (gur gum) stod du 'tshangs pa sel lo //
T16TD4441E:354a-13: ni ra guntha'i khu bas rta byas zos na bud med dbang du 'dus so //
T16TD4441E:354a-14: sbrang rtsi dang mnyam du btang na lce'i dog sel lo //
T16TD4441E:354a-15: ko ci la 'bras tsam re dang mnyam du btang na skra rgya sma ra sogs dkar por song ba slar yang nag por 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354a-16: ni ra gunda'i khung dang mnyam du zos na skya rbab sel bar 'gyur zhing chu nad tsha grang gang la yang phan no //
T16TD4441E:354a-17: ha la dhi dang mnyam du btang na khrag mkhris kyi nad zhi bar byed do //
T16TD4441E:354a-18: ha la dhi dang mnyam du ba mar la sbyar nas lba ba la byugs na skem par 'gyur ro /
T16TD4441E:354a-19: kha mdog gcig ma'i mar la sbyar nas mig la byugs na 'dre gdon gang gis kyang gnod pa mi 'byung ngo //
T16TD4441E:354a-20: til mar la sbyar (sga ser) nas mig la byugs na mig gi nad thams cad la phan (sga ser) zhing gsal bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354a-21: ni ra gunda'i khu bar sbyar la snar blug na yams mgo phyed na ba sel lo //
T16TD4441E:354a-22: ba dar gyis rta byas btang na dmu rdzings kyi nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:354a-23: tu la se ka (tu la se'i mi tog) pa ta dang mnyam du zos na tsha ba'i nad thams cad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:354b-0: tsa ra tsi ri dang mnyam du zos na stobs glang po dang mnyam par @354b 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354b-3: bee ri gsum gyi khu ba zho bzhi re dang mnyam du zos na dangs ma 'phel zhing lus stobs che la mdangs gsal zhing gzhon sha chags pa sogs phan yon dpag tu med do //
T16TD4441E:354b-4: de rnams ni sa mu dra pha la kha sgyur dang bcas pa'o //
T16TD4441E:354b-13: shun pa rnams so sor zho drug cu re gnyis ra /
T16TD4441E:354b-14: nag ri mu sa ri zho lnga bcu nga dgu /
T16TD4441E:354b-15: tsa ka ba dza gzho nyi shu rtsa drug / d'a li tsi ni zho bco lnga rnams zhib par btags la /
T16TD4441E:354b-16: bu ram zho drug brgya dang mnyam du 'dres par (li khri aa ru ra ba ru ra skyu ru ra) snur la legs par 'dres pa dang ril bu sum brgya bsgril la /
T16TD4441E:354b-17: de nas snga dro zas gang yang ma zos pa'i sngon du ril bu re nyin ltar gyis zla ba (shing tsha) gcig gi bar zos na khog nang gi nad thams cad zhi bar 'gyur la /
T16TD4441E:354b-18: zla ba gnyis kyi bar du zos na lus yang bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354b-19: zla ba gsum gyi bar du zos na mdangs gsal /
T16TD4441E:354b-20: zla ba bzhi'i bar du zos na stobs 'phel /
T16TD4441E:354b-21: zla ba lnga'i bar du zos na skra dkar por song ba skra nag por 'gyur /
T16TD4441E:354b-22: zla ba drug gi bar du zos na lus rgyags par 'gyur /
T16TD4441E:354b-23: zla ba bdun gyi bar du zos na gla ba'i mig ltar gsal bar 'gyur la /
T16TD4441E:354b-24: zla ba brgyad kyi bar du zos na sems dran pa gsal zhing sngar brjed pa rnams kyang dran par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354b-25: zla ba dgu'i bar du zos na rgyang ring po yang mig gis mthong bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:354b-26: zla ba bcu'i bar du zos na sa 'og gi gter mang po rnyed par 'gyur ba sogs yon tan mtha' yas so //
T16TD4441E:354b-33: bhangga ra rnams so so nas srang bco lnga re /
T16TD4441E:354b-34: sadzdzha khar dang lu ha tsurna gnyis zho bcu gnyis re /
T16TD4441E:354b-35: te dza ba la zho gsum /
T16TD4441E:354b-36: simba ri ...(ma nu rta rkang) zho bzhi rnams zhib par btags la bu ram rnying pa srang drug cu dang /
T16TD4441E:354b-37: (aa ru ra ba ru ra skyu ru ra thal dkar rdo rje) mnyam du snur la legs (li khri) par 'dres pa dang ril bu sum brgya bsgril (zi tsha) la de nas snga dro lto (lcags phye) stong la ril bu re nyin ltar gyis zla ba gcig gi /
T16TD4441E:355a-0: @355a * // bar zos pas khong nang gi nad dang mi gtsang ba mtha' dag dbyung ste lus shel gong ltar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355a-1: zla ba gnyis kyi bar zos na mdangs gsal bar 'gyur /
T16TD4441E:355a-2: zla ba gsum gyi bar du zos na lus stobs dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355a-3: zla ba bzhi'i bar du zos na bad kan gyi nad thams cad rtsa ba nas thon par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355a-4: zla ba lnga'i bar du zos na skra dang kha spu dkar por song ba slar nag por 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355a-5: zla ba drug gi bar du zos na so don pa slar skye bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355a-6: zla ba bdun gyi bar du zos na mig shin tu gsal zhing rgyang ring po 'ang mthong bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355a-7: zla ba brgyad kyi bar du zos na mdze'i rigs thams cad rtsa ba nas thon par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355a-8: zla ba dgu'i bar du zos na dangs ma shin tu 'phel zhing lus gzi brjid dang ldan la 'dod pa'ang ci 'dod spyod nus par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355a-9: zla ba bcu'i bar du zos na mngon par shes pa thogs med 'byung ba sogs phan yon bsam pa'i rab las 'das so //
T16TD4441E:355a-10: pa lag sha la brten pa'i man ngag khyad par can kun la med pa'i khyad chos /
T16TD4441E:355a-11: slob dpon ha ri ha ri bha tsi'i gdams pa zab mo ni /
T16TD4441E:355a-12: pa la sha ba dze'i snum legs par bton la /
T16TD4441E:355a-14: sbrang rtsi se ba phyed gnyis /
T16TD4441E:355a-15: ba mar se ba do ste yongs sgril se ba bzhi'i rtsis re grangs ltar chags rgyun du zos na nyin mo'ang skar ma thams cad mthong /
T16TD4441E:355a-16: tshe ring thung lha dang mnyam /
T16TD4441E:355a-17: gzhan gyis mthong na (ba la sha'i 'bru) lus shin tu ring zhing sbom pa blos mi 'khyud pa tsam du mthong /
T16TD4441E:355a-18: gzi brjid nyi ma dang mnyam pas gzhan gyis glags lta bar mi nus /
T16TD4441E:355a-19: lus mdzes shing blta na sdug pa 'dod lha dang mnyam /
T16TD4441E:355a-20: gang 'dod du bsam pa tsam gyis sleb /
T16TD4441E:355a-21: glo gros phur bu dang mnyam /
T16TD4441E:355a-22: gang smras kun gyis bden par 'dzin zhing nyan ba dga' byed dpa' bo dang mtshungs /
T16TD4441E:355a-23: lus la gzhan gang gis kyang gnod pas mi tshugs /
T16TD4441E:355a-24: rang nyid lus 'dor bar 'dod na ma gtogs stobs rtsal dang ldan par bskal ba grangs med kyi bar du gnas par 'gyur /
T16TD4441E:355a-25: yang tho rangs gong bzhin la /
T16TD4441E:355a-26: phyi dro pa la sha'i rtsa ba //
T16TD4441E:355b-2: me tog /'bras bu lnga cha mnyam zhib par btags pa se ba bzhi /
T16TD4441E:355b-3: ba mar dang sbrang rtsi se ba do re bcas zos na sa gzhir rkang pa khru gang tsam ma reg par bar snang la 'gro //
T16TD4441E:355b-4: lcags sa dang zangs me la bsregs par dri chu bran na gser du 'gyur /
T16TD4441E:355b-5: lus la grib ma ma 'byung ba sogs yon tan dpag tu med pa thob /
T16TD4441E:355b-6: da yang thog mar sman btang nas lo bcu gnyis tshun gong gi rtags de rnams rdzogs par rim can du 'byung ngo //
T16TD4441E:355b-7: thog ma sman sbyor ba dang za ba gnyis ka gza' skar legs pa la byed do //
T16TD4441E:355b-8: nad gsar rnying cha grang gang la'ang sbyongs 'gro ba'i rigs la gtong na /
T16TD4441E:355b-9: bi da ra zhib par btags la zho gsum chu skol gyis phul la btang nas lus ma 'khyags pa byas /
T16TD4441E:355b-10: de nas ma dag par chu skol gyis lcag rim bzhin rgyab la gcod mtshams su sleb pa dang rkang lag chu grang mos bkrus par chod la /
T16TD4441E:355b-11: rjes kyi zas spyod sogs sbyong spyi dang 'dra'o //
T16TD4441E:355b-19: pippa la ka mu la shunthi /
T16TD4441E:355b-20: si la dza ta rnams srang re /
T16TD4441E:355b-21: ha ri ta ka srang lnga rnams zhib par btags la bu ram srang bco lngas rta byas ril bu skyu ru ra tsam sgril la chu skol bzhi cha bsdus pa tsam (dbyi mong) gyis phul (pho ris drod sman byi thang ka shug pa rgyam tsha pi pi ling gi rtsa ba lga) nas tho rangs btang bas pho ba mi bde ba /
T16TD4441E:355b-28: pho ba spos 'khrog / kha dri mi zhim pa /
T16TD4441E:355b-30: 'dus pa rnams la mchog tu phan zhing dang kha 'byed par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:355b-31: ka ka dzam gi'i rtsa ba nad pa'i chu la brdar nas rma gang yod la byugs pas mda' gri phog pa sogs ma gsar rnying kun bsos shing khrag kyang chad do //
T16TD4441E:355b-32: khyi smyo ba dang ma smyo ba gang gis rmugs kyang /
T16TD4441E:355b-33: tsa ra tsi ri'i lo ma phyed dang gsum /
T16TD4441E:355b-34: bu ram ba ru ra tsam de dang mnyam du khong du btang zhing /
T16TD4441E:355b-35: lo ma chur brdar ba rma khar yang byugs pas rma myur du bsos zhing khyi dug gi gnod pa yang mi 'byung ngo //
T16TD4441E:356a-8: chang zho bcu bzhu ba'i nang du dngul chu zho //
T16TD4441E:356a-9: sa pa dang rdza'i spar [?] bu lta bu khebs ldan gyi nang tshva zhib mos brgyangs pa'i dkyil du bcug nas kha legs par bcad /
T16TD4441E:356a-10: (gsha' dkar la sogs pa btul ma 'di rnams sman sbyor gang dang gang gi skabs su de dang de btul dgos pa byung na so so'i kha sgyur rnams dor te btags par) x thug nas phyed tsam gyis gtums /
T16TD4441E:356a-11: de nas sa dong khru gang tsam zhig brus la ra'i ril mas bkang ba'i dkyil du bcug / de la me sbar te me ma yal tsam la slar yang ril ma bsnan te zhag gsum gyi x xx x ba'i khu ba srang lnga dang mnyam du blugs la kha legs par bsdams nas kha mtshams 'jim pas byugs la rlung mi 'gro bar byas te nyin phyed tsam gyi bar shing gi me mtshams ma chad par btang /
T16TD4441E:356a-12: de nas bton la grang thag chod thog rdo gzhong gi nang du zhib par btags /
T16TD4441E:356a-13: thog mar gro tsam re dang /
T16TD4441E:356a-14: de nas sran ma tsam re dz'a ti'i bzhi cha re dang mnyam du btang na lus stobs 'phel /
T16TD4441E:356a-16: gzhon sha chags pa sogs yon tan mtha' yas pa 'byung ngo //
T16TD4441E:356a-18: singga ra pha srang do bil ba'i 'bras bu'i kha nas mtheb gang tsam ma chags pa sgor ba'i nang du blug / de nas sgor ba des kha bcad /
T16TD4441E:356a-19: ras brdungs pa bsres pa'i 'jim pa sbyin po'i srab mthug nas gang tsam gyis gtums /
T16TD4441E:356a-20: de nas sa dong brus la ra'i ril ma'i nang na me gtong lugs yun tshad sogs (rgya mtshal) gong bzhin tshar ba dang bton /
T16TD4441E:356a-21: 'jim pa la sogs gang legs par byas rjes rgya mtshal bil ba dang dbyer med song ba de rdo gzhong gi nang du legs par snur la sran ma tsam re li shi rdog bzhi tsam btags pa dang mnyam du btang kyang yon tan gong dang 'dra'o //
T16TD4441E:356a-23: aa bha ...(lhang tsher) ka srang lnga /
T16TD4441E:356b-0: snum bton pa'i ro ma ba chu srang bcu dang mnyam du legs par brdungs te srab mthug bag leb tsam @356b byas la skam thag chod pa dang gci ba'i me'i dkyil du nyin phyed tsam gyi bar bsregs /
T16TD4441E:356b-1: de nas bton la grang thag chod pa dang gi la ko ti'i khu ba dang mnyam du rdo gzhong nang du nyin gcig gi ring brdar te slar yang srab mthug bag leb tsam bzos /
T16TD4441E:356b-2: de skam thag chod pa dang gong bzhin gci ba'i me nang du nyin phyed kyi bar bsregs /
T16TD4441E:356b-3: ma he ri'i khu bas nyin gcig gi bar nyed pa dang bag leb tsam bcos nas gci ba'i mer bsregs pa sogs sngar bzhin byas /
T16TD4441E:356b-4: ban bu thi'i khu ba dang mnyam du nyed pa sogs gzhan ma gong dang 'dra ba la gci ba'i me nang du nyin gcig gi bar bsregs la /
T16TD4441E:356b-5: de nas grang thag chod pa dang bton la rdo gzhong nang du zhib par btags la ras la btsags /
T16TD4441E:356b-6: de nas 'bras tsam re li shi bzhi tsam brdungs pa'i phye ma dang mnyam du btang bas lus rgyags pa /
T16TD4441E:356b-10: 'dod pa spyod nus pa sogs stobs bskyed kun gyi mchog tu 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:356b-12: tamba mang nyung ji ltar 'dod pa sbrang gshog legs par 'then te mer bsregs /
T16TD4441E:356b-13: de snum gyi dkyil du bcug / yang mer bsregs /
T16TD4441E:356b-14: snum nang du 'jug pa sogs lan bdun gyi bar byas /
T16TD4441E:356b-15: de bzhin du rim pa ltar ;
T16TD4441E:356b-18: ba'i zho star bu'i khu ba rnams lan bdun (zangs) re byas rjes /
T16TD4441E:356b-19: de nas rdza snod du ra'i chu zangs mang nyung dang bstun pa'i snod kyi phyed tsam gang ba blug la me btang ste /
T16TD4441E:356b-20: chu de skam thag chod pa dang chu gtsang mas legs par bkrus /
T16TD4441E:356b-21: de nas dngul chu zangs leb gang yod kyi phyi nang tshang mar mdog dkar por ma song bar byugs /
T16TD4441E:356b-22: de steng bhangga ri'i khu ba legs par byugs /
T16TD4441E:356b-23: de nas zangs dang ljid mnyam pa'i mu zi ser po btags pa zangs brtsegs pa'i srubs la khod snyoms yod pa byas nas khog ma gsar pa'i nang du bcug /
T16TD4441E:356b-24: khog ma'i kha dam par bcad de kha mtshams 'jim pas gtums nas rlung mi 'gro bar bya /
T16TD4441E:356b-25: de lcags sgyed lta bu'i steng du bzhag nas nyin gnyis dang mtshan gcig gi bar me mtshams mchad par btang /
T16TD4441E:356b-26: de yang nyin dang po la me cung zad chung ba btang /
T16TD4441E:357a-1: phyi ma gnyis la shin tu tsha ba btang /
T16TD4441E:357a-2: de nas grang thag chod pa dang ras kyi khud du gtums nas chu gtsang mar 'jug 'don thengs lnga tsam byas /
T16TD4441E:357a-3: de rjes skam thag chod pa dang rdo gzhong du zhib par btags /
T16TD4441E:357a-4: de nas 'bras tsam re nam zla grang dus li shi dang /
T16TD4441E:357a-5: dro dus ka ko la dang mnyam du btang bas pho ba'i me drod ches cher bskyed de zas gang zos kyang 'phral du 'ju bas dang kha shin tu bde la lus gzi mdangs dang stobs rtsal che zhing gzhon sha chags pa sogs yon tan dpag tu med pa 'byung ngo //
T16TD4441E:357a-7: lu ha mang nyung ji ltar 'dod pa srab 'thug nas phyed tsam brdungs pa sor bzhi gru bzhi tsam pa bcos /
T16TD4441E:357a-8: de rdza snod kyi nang du bi sa kha pa ri'i khu ba dang mnyam du blug la nyi ma gang tsha sar zhag nyi shu'i bar khu ba skam rim bzhin blug nas bzhag / zhag grangs them pa dang bton la slar yang gong (lcags) bzhin la phug btsir ba'i khu ba dang mnyam du zhag nyi shu'i bar bzhag / de nas bton la sol ba'i me nang du skam pas bzung la dmar por tshig pa dang ba'i chu'i nang du bcug / slar yang sreg 'jug gong bzhin lan lnga'i bar byas la /
T16TD4441E:357a-9: de nas rdo gzhong nang du zhib par btags la nas tsam re nam zla grong dus lga dang /
T16TD4441E:357a-10: dro dus ka ko la dang mnyam du zos pas dangs ma 'phel zhing lus stobs bskyed la /
T16TD4441E:357a-11: mu sa ba ra dang mnyam du zos na dmu rdzings dang skya rbab sel /
T16TD4441E:357a-12: aa ka ra ka dang la bangga cha mnyam btags pa se ba phyed do dang /
T16TD4441E:357a-13: gong gi lcags phye se ba phyed bcas btang na dang kha mi bde ba /
T16TD4441E:357a-15: mig ser rnams la phan no /
T16TD4441E:357a-16: zha nye nag po 'dul thabs ni /
T16TD4441E:357a-17: shi sha mang nyung ji ltar 'dod pa srab mthug ras tsam brdungs pa sen mo tsam du gtubs /
T16TD4441E:357a-18: (li shi) de dang ljid mnyam pa'i pippa la dang mnyam du rdo gzhong nang du nyin gnyis kyi bar skam nyed zhib par byas /
T16TD4441E:357a-19: de nas ras la btsags pa se ba phyed shel dkar dang li shi cha mnyam (zha nye nag po) du btags pa zho re dang mnyam du btang na /
T16TD4441E:357b-0: lus shin tu rid cing shed med pa sogs la mdangs dang lus (drod sman) stobs mchog @357b tu bzang bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:357b-2: sa ta ji ltar 'dod pa lcags snod du bzhu ba de dang ljid mnyam pa'i bku tsi zhib par btags pa thug thal ltar 'debs shing dkrug / de legs par 'dres nas nas bangs [?] pa dang rdo gzhong nang du zhib par btags la ras la btsags pa se ba phyed shel dkar dang ka ko la cha mnyam (gsha' tshe) du btags pa se ba bzhi dang mnyam du btang na tsha ba'i nad rigs thams cad la phan no //
T16TD4441E:357b-4: ha ri ta la ta ba ki srang nyi shu zhib par btags la ras la gtums khog mar gong gi 'bras chu skyur mo'i nang du bcug la ras khog ma'i mthil lam reg pa'i ngos ras thum chu dkyil du yong ba'i thi gu ri thung 'tsham pa btags pa'i shing tshag khog ma'i khar 'jog / khog ma lcags sgyed lta bu'i steng du /
T16TD4441E:357b-5: (bab la bcag na cig pu ltar shun pa 'bye rgyu yod pa zhig yod) bzhag nas me nyin phyed kyi ring bar ma chad par btang /
T16TD4441E:357b-6: de nas bton la rdo gzhong nang du aa dzya pa la srang do dang mnyam ras shing gi rtsa bas khu ba byas la nyin gsum gyi bar du snur /
T16TD4441E:357b-7: de bzhin du pa la sha'i khu ba /
T16TD4441E:357b-11: ba ta ku ai'i khu ba rnams kyis rim pa bzhin nyin gsum re'i bar snur la /
T16TD4441E:357b-12: de nas srab 'thug bag lo tsam byas la skam /
T16TD4441E:357b-13: de nas khog ma'i nang du pa la sha brdar ba'i phye mas khog ma'i phyed brgyangs pa'i steng du bzhag / de steng du yang shing phye khengs par blug la kha gcod legs par 'grig pa'i mtshams 'jim pas gtums nas rlung mi 'chor ba byas /
T16TD4441E:357b-14: de lcags sgyed kyi steng du bzhag la thog mar nyin phyed kyi bar me chung ba rta ma chad tsam re btang /
T16TD4441E:357b-15: de nas nyin phyed kyi bar de las che tsam btang /
T16TD4441E:357b-16: de nas nyin mtshan gnyis kyi ring me shin tu tsha ba btang /
T16TD4441E:357b-17: de nas grang thag chod pa dang bton la rdo gzhong gi nang du zhib par btags la ras la btsags pa se ba phyed dang hla dhi (lga ser) zho do dang mnyam du zos na khrag mkhris kyi nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:357b-18: ba yi bi (byi thang ka) rangga zho gang ha la dhi zho do bcas zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gi ring zos na skom pa'i nad sel bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:358a-1: thang chu zho lnga dang sendha lo na zho gang bcas pa zla gcig zhag bcu dgu'i bar zos na mdze dkar po'i rigs rtsa ba nas thon no /
T16TD4441E:358a-2: pippa la zho do dang aa ja wa na zho lnga bcas pa zhag grangs gong 'dra zos na pags nad shu 'gram sogs sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358a-3: ba ku tsi dang na gi zho gsum re bcas pa zla gcig zhag bcu dgu'i (rgyam tsha) bar zos na mdze nag po'i rigs rtsa ba nas thon no //
T16TD4441E:358a-4: ja ya ba tri dang khu ra sa aa dza wa ni zho re bcas pa (drod sman la la phud) zhag grangs gong 'dra zos na sha bkra'i nad sal lo //
T16TD4441E:358a-5: ni ra gundi'i khu ba zho gsum /
T16TD4441E:358a-6: la bangga zho lnga dang bcas pa zla ba gcig zhag bcu dgu'i bar zos na mdzes sor mo gum pa dang yan lag zha ba sogs sos so /
T16TD4441E:358a-7: (/ ja ti'i me tog la la phug chung ba) shve ta su ba ri dang ma ri tsi zho re bcas pa zhag grangs gong 'dra zos na khrag la brten pa'i mdze la phan no //
T16TD4441E:358a-8: pippa la'i pags pa dang ja (li shi) mu ni'i pags pa zho gsum re bcas pa zla gcig zhag bcu dgu'i bar zos na mdzes sor mo 'am yan lag chad pa dang /
T16TD4441E:358a-9: sna chad pa zhom (go yu bcag na kha dog dkar po yod pa pho ris) pa sogs sos so //
T16TD4441E:358a-10: pa la lo tsa na dang pa na zho re bcas pa zhag (drod sman) grangs gong bzhin zos na rlung la brten pa'i yan lag zha grum /
T16TD4441E:358a-11: grang ba sogs bsos par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:358a-12: sbrang rtsi dang mnyam du zhag bcu bzhi'i bar zos na 'dus pa'i nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358a-13: la wangga se ba bzhi dang mnyam du zhag grangs gong 'dra zos na bse dug gi nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358a-14: pippa la dang sendha lo na zho re /
T16TD4441E:358a-15: la wangga zho do dang bcas zla ba gcig zhag bcu dgu'i bar zos na dmu rdzings kyi nad thams cad sel bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:358a-18: gu ra gsum zho do dang (li shi) bcas pa zhag grangs gong bzhin zos na mgo gzer gyi nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358a-19: shunthi dang aa sa gandha (drod sman rgya tsha) zho re dang bcas (li shi) ba zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gi bar zos na khong nang gi rlung skran zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:358a-21: hir [?] bi'i khu ba zho gang (drod sman thur ma) dang bcas pa zla gcig gam zhag bcu dgu'i bar du zos na mdze rigs thams cad rtsa ba nas thon no//
T16TD4441E:358a-22: (lga ba spru ba) / pippa la ...(drod sman) dang da dhu ra'i ...(thang phrom) khu ba zho re /
T16TD4441E:358b-0: pan @358b dum tsam dang bcas pa zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gi bar du zos na sgrags pa dang 'byin pa sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358b-1: ae randa'i rtsa ba dang yi bi rangga zho do re /
T16TD4441E:358b-2: dza ye pha la zho gang dang bcas pa nyin bcu bzhi'i bar zos na srin nad rtsa ba nas 'byin no //
T16TD4441E:358b-3: na ga da ba ni'i rtsa ba /
T16TD4441E:358b-5: shunthi gsum zho do ra dang bcas pa zla gcig zhag bcu dgu'i bar zos na rtsa 'dar gyi nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358b-6: bangga na'i khu ba zho (danda byi thang) do dang mnyam du (dz'a ti) zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gi bar zos na sna'i nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358b-7: ti ta ba ro la'i khu ba zho do //
T16TD4441E:358b-8: rangga ni'i khu ba zho drug dang bcas pa nyin (lga) bcu bzhi'i bar zos na mtshan bar rdol ba'i nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358b-10: aa dza wa ni zho brgyad dang bcas pa zhag nyer gcig gi bar btang na gzhang 'brum gyi nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358b-11: pippa la'i khu ba zho do dang mnyam (gser me) du zos na mri gi'i nad sel lo //
T16TD4441E:358b-12: tsa ra tsi ri'i khu ba dang /
T16TD4441E:358b-13: shunthi zho gsum re dang bcas pa zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gi par zos na za phrug gi nad sel lo /
T16TD4441E:358b-14: (/ la la phud) sbrang rtsi dang rangga ni zho gsum re dang bcas pa zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gi bar zos kyang phan yon gong dang 'dra'o //
T16TD4441E:358b-15: de rnams ni bab la btul ma kha bsgyur dang bcas pa'i phan yon te /
T16TD4441E:358b-16: sman de (lga) rnams gtong ring ro skyur ba dang la bug mi bza'/
T16TD4441E:358b-17: khyad par mdze nad kyi rigs la gtong skabs zas gang la 'ang tsha bsrung dgos so //
T16TD4441E:358b-18: gsha' dkar ram zha nye dkar po 'dul lugs ni /
T16TD4441E:358b-19: gsha' dkar rangga srang phyed gsum srab mthug shog bu tsam brdungs pa sen mo tsam du gtubs /
T16TD4441E:358b-20: aa dza wa ni dang be da ha gnyis srang nyi shu re so sor zhib par btags la gci ba khru gang gru bzhi tsam brtsegs pa'i steng du ras bting /
T16TD4441E:358b-21: de steng gong gi la la phud kyi phye ma'i phyed snyoms par brdal de steng ba ru ra'i phye ma'i phyed snyoms par bting /
T16TD4441E:358b-22: de steng gong gi zha nye dkar po bkram /
T16TD4441E:358b-23: (la la phud) de steng (ba tur) la la phud kyi phyi ma phyed po brdal /
T16TD4441E:358b-24: de steng ba ru ra'i phye ma phyed po brdal la gci ba'i me sbar te me ma yal bar bzhag / grang thag chod pa dang zha nye dkar po rnams sgrugs la rdo gzhong du zhib par btags te ras la btsags pa se ba gang /
T16TD4441E:359a-0: ae la ya tsi se ba gang dang shel @359a * //
T16TD4441E:359a-1: dkar zho gang bcas zla ba gcig gi bar btang na lus rgyags pa /
T16TD4441E:359a-5: rgas kha sra ba sogs yon tan dpag tu med cing stobs bskyed kyi mchog tu 'gyur ro //
T16TD4441E:359a-6: de ltar slob dpon kun phan bdud rtsi byin gyis mdzad pa'i tshangs pa'i rig byed rgya mtsho'i yan lag 'dzin pa g-yo ba can dang /
T16TD4441E:359a-7: lha dbang phyug gis tshogs bdag la gnang ba'i sa mu dra pha la'i sbyor ba sogs zur bskol zab gnad can sna tshogs dang bcas sbyor ba kha bsgyur sdom pa sum brgyar nye ba'i bstan bcos 'di ni /
T16TD4441E:359a-8: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi mkhyen brtse nus ba'i spyi gzugs rgyal ba'i dbang po thams cad mkhyen gzigs chen po'i bla'i sman pa /
T16TD4441E:359a-9: deng dus bsil ldan gyi ljongs 'dir gso ba rig pa'i ring lugs 'dzin pa la 'gran pa'i zla thams cad dang bral ba yar stod dar mo sman rams pa blo bzang chos grags kyis 'di ltar sgyur cig zhes bka' stsal autpa la'i chun po thod du bcings te 'phags yul ma thu rar rgyal rigs mchog gi rigs las tshe'i rig byed 'dzin par gu n'a tha dang /
T16TD4441E:359a-10: gtsang stod 'dar gyi skad gnyis pa ngag dbang phun tshogs lhun grub kyis rab byung bcu gcig pa'i nang gi don 'grub ces pa sa lug nag pas nya ba'i yar tshes dge bar phun tshogs lugs brgya'i mdun sa pho brang chen po po ta lar bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'i yi ge pa ni nyang stod pa 'jam dbyangs dbang pos bgyis pa 'dis kyang 'gro ba mang po la phan par gyur cig / shu bha mastu sarba dza ga tam /
